# Break video clips are NOT committed — typical free-stock licenses restrict
# redistributing the raw files (a public repo would do that). The folder is kept
# via its README; drop royalty-free clips in locally and the app picks them up.
# (Truly CC0 / public-domain clips are fine to commit — add exceptions below.)
Horizon/Horizon/BreakVideos/*.mp4
Horizon/Horizon/BreakVideos/*.mov
Horizon/Horizon/BreakVideos/*.m4v
Horizon/Horizon/BreakVideos/CREDITS.txt

# Misc
*.log
